{"type": "article", "id": 8311, "title": "Lexon 数码产品系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-10T07:19:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234717XMD5wVhueS93Lx2a.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这是设计师 Pauline Deltour 为 Lexon 设计的一个数码产品系列。包括蓝牙音箱，移动电源，名片夹和 U 盘钥匙扣。这一系列产品的设计来源是 20 世纪初期巴黎人优雅的手包和混合型的都市生活态度。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t设计师采用优雅的配色和简约的设计，处处为女性考虑周全。如蓝牙音箱的扬声器呈管状，且需要通过旋转来进行开关或调节声音大小，设计得像是一支口红。而移动电源外缠绕着整齐得橡胶松紧带，极大避免了移动电源从手里滑落。名片夹的两个卡片之间用一个小镜子分隔，可用悄悄拿来补妆，钥匙扣小巧可爱，小口哨形状的 U 盘也充满了女性俏皮的气质。<a href=\"http://www.lexon-design.com/capsules/fine.html\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052347141qNPe8pLWmEVItjD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.69070905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523471405vUVfLjgl6R1pJC.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67237164\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234714BmMl15zL3cfPOu7h.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67481663\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234715NFlKsBU5SZ8WucOR.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66259169\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234715pRdwQhlYVk6eXUAM.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.68704156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234716IihyAGTBPjkm3rSQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.79706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234716p34wkEVXol5yG8Ri.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}